               GUILTY
            </rs>, <rs id="t17850914-25-punish124" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17850914-25-punish124" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850914-25-defend323 t17850914-25-punish124"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>He was humbly recommended to mercy by the Prosecutor and Jury.</p>
